originalText.text: Dr. Nawlo's many years of experience are apparent in his workmanship. He takes his time to ensure I am comfortable, and thoroughly explains to me step by step what he is doing to put me at ease. He is very gentle which is important for my super sensitive gum line. Would definitely recommend to anyone who is scared of getting dental work done.
